      "duration": 1.47,
      "size": 23472,
      "text": "把它的各位数字加起来，得到一个更小的数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "digital-root",
      "section_id": "define",
      "line_id": "def-1",
      "filename": "define-def-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/digital-root/define-def-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.68,
      "size": 26928,
      "text": "这个最终剩下的一位数，就叫做原数的数字根。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "digital-root",
      "section_id": "define",
      "line_id": "def-2",
      "filename": "define-def-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/digital-root/define-def-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.94,
      "size": 31104,
      "text": "无论数字多大，反复相加总会坍缩到一到九之间。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "digital-root",
      "section_id": "mod9",
      "line_id": "mod-1",
      "filename": "mod9-mod-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/digital-root/mod9-mod-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.9,
      "size": 30384,
      "text": "因为十除以九余一，每一位的权重对九取余都是一。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "digital-root",
      "section_id": "mod9",
      "line_id": "mod-2",
      "filename": "mod9-mod-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/digital-root/mod9-mod-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.29,
      "size": 36720,
      "text": "所以各位之和与原数对九同余，数字根其实就是模九的结果。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "digital-root",
      "section_id": "mod9",
      "line_id": "mod-3",
      "filename": "mod9-mod-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/digital-root/mod9-mod-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.67,
      "size": 26784,
      "text": "只是当余数为零时，我们把数字根记成九。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "digital-root",
      "section_id": "casting",
      "line_id": "cast-1",
      "filename": "casting-cast-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/digital-root/casting-cast-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.86,
      "size": 29808,
      "text": "古人用这个性质来检查算术，叫做弃九验算。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "digital-root",
      "section_id": "casting",
      "line_id": "cast-3",
      "filename": "casting-cast-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/digital-root/casting-cast-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.09,
      "size": 33408,
      "text": "如果和答案的数字根不一致，那这道题一定算错了。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "digital-root",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/digital-root/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.66,
      "size": 26496,
      "text": "输入一个数，看它一步步坍缩到自己的数字根。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "digital-root",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/digital-root/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.92,
      "size": 30672,
      "text": "再输入一道加法或乘法，让弃九法替你把把关。"
    },
    {
